Folders:
'bundling' - folder with the main bundle and all installed bundle
'*' - bundle

Bundle extension:
'final.bundle.scss' - main bundle
'*.bundle.scss' - bundle for * bundle



How to create custom packet:
1) Create a folder 'bundle_name'
2) Write css/scss in this folder (OPTIONAL: Create sub-folder 'bundling' for cleaner bundling)

3) Create a file "bundle_name.bundle.scss"
4) Write bundling logic inside this file

5) Put folder 'bundle_name' inside folder 'resources/css/'
6) Put file 'bundle_name.bundle.scss' inside folder 'resources/css/bundling/'
7) In 'resources/css/bundling/final.bundle.scss' at the end of all imports put: @import 'bundle_name.bundle';
